results.QaldSentence: In which countries do people speak Japanese?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Country ; dbo:language res:Japanese_language }

results.QaldSentence: Which of Tim Burton's films had the highest budget?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:director res:Tim_Burton ; dbo:budget ?b } ORDER BY ?b OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

results.QaldSentence: Which museum in New York has the most visitors?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Museum ; dbo:location res:New_York_City ; dbo:numberOfVisitors ?num } ORDER BY DESC(?num) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

results.QaldSentence: What was the first Queen album?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Album ; dbo:artist <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queen_(band)> ; dbo:releaseDate ?d } ORDER BY ASC(?d) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

results.QaldSentence: What was the first name of the band Queens of the Stone Age?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?name WHERE { res:Queens_of_the_Stone_Age dbo:alias ?name }

results.QaldSentence: What was the last movie with Alec Guinness?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:starring res:Alec_Guinness ; dbo:releaseDate ?date } ORDER BY DESC(?date) LIMIT 1

results.QaldSentence: Give me all actors starring in Last Action Hero
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Last_Action_Hero dbo:starring ?uri }

results.QaldSentence: Who discovered Pluto?
results.QaldSparql: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?uri WHERE { dbr:Pluto dbo:discoverer ?uri }
